annotationA: Uncharacterized protein, isoform B; It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of mitotic metaphase/anaphase transition; regulation of establishment of planar polarity
annotationB: Cell division cycle 27 is a component of the anaphase-promoting complex/cyclosome (APC/C). It is important for substrate recruitment and interacts with its co-activators, fzy and rap, as well as the mitotic checkpoint proteins, mad2 and BubR1
